name: Simmons_Upholstery_Kingsley_Beige_Large_Sectional_and_Ottoman
description: Create a warm, inviting seating area with the Simmons Upholstery Kingsley Sectional and matching ottoman. This neutral three-piece sectional has a transitional style with flared arms and deep, welted seat cushions that are reversible. With sinuous wire springs and high-density foam seat cushions, you can sit back and relax in comfort or invite friends and family over for a night of entertaining. This sectional features Beautyrest Pocketed Coils in the seat cushions for added comfort and hardwood lumber in all load-bearing areas. StyleCasual, Traditional, Transitional, UrbanMaterialFabricAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBeigeFurniture PatternSolidProduct FeaturesOttoman Included
